{"tid":2064552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁凌杰逝世一年 今多區悼念  父：政權阻召死因庭","createTime":"2020-06-15T01:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T08:23:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"79a3cd450aa0aeca2704970965c3d4ecc664297c","tid":2064552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:49:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/ABDQ47JTQAYRCQOEP44TT4SU5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FABDQ47JTQAYRCQOEP44TT4SU5Q%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=56941f21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FABDQ47JTQAYRCQOEP44TT4SU5Q%2F&h=b4ce6323\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/ABDQ47JTQAYRCQOEP44TT4SU5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n梁凌杰逝世一年 今多區悼念 <br />\n父：政權阻召死因庭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一年前的今日，年僅35歲的梁凌杰以死相諫政府撤回《逃犯條例》，成為反送中運動首名犧牲的抗爭者。本報取得梁父錄音，訴說過去一年過得絕不容易，冀望展開死因研訊，追尋兒子墮樓當天有否遇過任何不公義的冷待，但「面對政權百般阻撓，我哋束手無策，但我哋唔會放棄」。時光荏苒，港人無忘記梁凌杰的犧牲，以白絲帶黑衣為記，相約在多區設壇，向梁獻花致意。 <br />\n<br />\n記者：李詠希 張雅婷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VJYR2KEH7XIBTPLUUE7ATEOXUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVJYR2KEH7XIBTPLUUE7ATEOXUE.jpg&h=21f0e2d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一年前的今日，身穿黃色雨衣的梁凌杰在太古廣場掛上標語橫額示威，最終墮樓身亡，成為運動首名犧牲的抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n梁父稱，兒子雖然已經離開，「思念一啲都無減退，同時為佢嘅崇高理念而自豪」。他至今仍希望為兒子取回公道，盼能展開死因研訊，「希望知道杰仔當天有冇得到應有嘅。。。。。。。。。。。。。。平、不公義、不為人知嘅冷待，正如呢一年警方冷待對我哋一樣」，他透露已將事件交律師處理。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，代表梁父的律師曾多次向警方發信，要求對方提交調查報告，包括驗屍報告及相關紀錄，但警方一直沒回應，只確認已收到律師來信。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S7XP7UHBDEZBT5GP2LMLZLYHB4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS7XP7UHBDEZBT5GP2LMLZLYHB4.gif&h=a00b9d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民陣秘書處今日會到梁凌杰墮樓的太古廣場外獻花。許頌明攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TG25A4IRIOD7AED4RSCVIZJDWE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTG25A4IRIOD7AED4RSCVIZJDWE.gif&h=7db3e075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁凌杰逝世翌日，發動反送中大遊行的民陣稱共「200萬+1人」上街追究警暴，成為香港歷史上最多人參與的遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">民陣籲穿黑衣繫白絲帶</span><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：梁父錄音全文<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆稱，已完成有關調查的詳細死因報告，稍後會提交死因裁判官及等候進一步指示是否。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。按需要考慮是否作出跟進；司法機構指不評論個別個案。<br />\n<br />\n梁凌杰逝世後翌日，觸發200萬名港人上街反對修例、追究警暴，成為香港歷史上最多人參與的遊行，人們當天行經事發地點太古廣場時，獻上白花致哀。發起當天遊行的民陣呼籲港人今天再穿黑衣、胸前繫白絲帶悼念梁凌杰，秘書處亦會到太古廣場外獻花，並在晚上9時，即梁凌杰墮樓一刻默哀。<br />\n<br />\n警方早前曾詢問民陣可否不要公開提及悼。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。跟進，悼念將如期舉行。警方或會阻撓悼念活動，但他反問：「唔通乜都唔做？」他指，一年過去，為香港受傷入獄人數甚多，若連悼念也不可，他寧願被捕。他促請警方尊重白事，切勿干預。<br />\n<br />\n旺角及屯門亦有區議員發起早上派發白絲帶街站、晚上於屯門公園入口設壇供市民向梁凌杰獻花致意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盼年輕人「留住有用身軀」<br />\n<br />\n學界方面，中學生連線呼籲各學校關注組在學校派發白絲帶給同學，讓同學返校佩戴。副主席阿恆表示，期望藉。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。「曉明街中學聯盟」更加會安排早上在觀塘曉明街足球場悼念，聯盟已經預計會有藍絲挑釁及警察干預，呼籲參加者保持冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n港人與梁凌杰擁抱同一理念抗爭，梁父看在眼內，亦感到心痛：「我同屋企人見到好多年輕人喺呢一年裏面，同杰仔一樣抱。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，睇住啲年輕人，感到好心痛同擔心，亦唔希望更多年輕人好似杰仔一樣，為呢個無希望嘅政權而受傷。」他盼年輕人能好好保護自己，「留住有用嘅身軀，行得更遠。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OA5ZVS7LWLISO5DEJ5VKAEN4NI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOA5ZVS7LWLISO5DEJ5VKAEN4NI.gif&h=a3ff4551&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6d403340042dd27ab4e6885467364d2b2b757da","tid":2064552,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f98a7c74c9f9464756a63ea82ec1fd119ef550a","tid":2064552,"uid":21028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:52:09.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街 死因庭都唔畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256cf06277552612d6df4b597e6d85307a078746","tid":2064552,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冀望展開死因研訊，追尋兒子墮樓當天有否遇過任何不公義的冷待，但「面對政權百般阻撓，我哋束手無策，但我哋唔會放棄」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班泛民偽法治大狀去咗邊？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"96fa80c1e89e39ef4eb9bb77a4b2e3c4233274a6","tid":2064552,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:55:09.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef39a78d6584211b8a118f3d834e11cf0ebbb0bf","tid":2064552,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"9點搞咁遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da16180dc210d1845a58f7302c2fd3f62e089c45","tid":2064552,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T01:57:07.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n一年喇，梁烈士"},{"pid":"19e17b835c40437a1a9734caea39ca98c3966924","tid":2064552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T03:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OA5ZVS7LWLISO5DEJ5VKAEN4NI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOA5ZVS7LWLISO5DEJ5VKAEN4NI.gif&h=a3ff4551&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ca46c7b6788007a28cd729896