:59:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8mZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=4474151a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a><br />\n<br />\nJune 15, 2020<br />\n時革1周年：全球19國、市聯手支援香港<br />\n梁凌杰先生逝世一年 - 6.15全城黑衣白絲帶日<br />\n6p 金鐘:梁凌杰先生離世一年悼念會<br />\n7p 天水圍:毋忘義士遺志 銀座悼念活動<br />\n7p 屯門:悼念梁凌杰烈士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金鐘:梁凌杰先生離世一年悼念會<br />\n發起人:民間自發<br />\n*全城黑衫 白絲帶<br />\n地點:金鐘太古廣場<br />\n時間:下午6點<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkrev.info/data/calendar/20200615-1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fdata%2Fcalendar%2F20200615-1.jpeg&h=5f8452bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n母忘義士遺志<br />\n銀座悼念活動<br />\n日期:2020年6月15日<br />\n時間:1900-2100<br />\n地點:銀座廣場<br />\n衣著:黑衣為記<br />\n天水連線<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkrev.info/data/calendar/20200615-3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fdata%2Fcalendar%2F20200615-3.jpeg&h=71727a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門:悼念梁凌杰烈士<br />\n發起人:民間自發<br />\n*現場會設壇供手足獻花致意<br />\n地點:屯門站屯門公園入口<br />\n時間:下午7點至晚上9點<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkrev.info/data/calendar/20200615-2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fdata%2Fcalendar%2F20200615-2.jpeg&h=66096e79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a594d369dde95cc2643cab3363e5783f30499dfb","tid":2064552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"秘書處亦會到太古廣場外獻花，並在晚上9時，即梁凌杰墮樓一刻默哀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img 